&lt;h2 class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Turn financial complexity into strategic impact!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Looking for a role where your analyses influence key business decisions? Coveo is looking for an Accounting Analyst to play a central role in the accounting treatment of strategic financial transactions, financial reporting, and continuous process improvement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;As a leader in artificial intelligence, we’re looking for someone who is curious, detail-oriented, and proactive. You’ll contribute to meaningful projects while helping automate and optimize financial processes across a growing global organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As our Accounting Analyst, you will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be responsible for the accounting, disclosure, and budgeting related to share-based compensation and equity transactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the preparation and monitoring of government tax credit and grant applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Transform financial data into actionable insights through ad hoc reporting and financial analyses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support statutory and tax compliance activities for our international subsidiaries across Canada, the United States, Europe, Australia, and beyond.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with multiple teams to address financial reporting and compliance needs while providing creative solutions to support business objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to a variety of cross-functional projects that help strengthen and scale our finance operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Here is what will qualify you for the role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have at least 2 years of experience in a similar accounting role, either in public practice or industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You hold a Chartered Professional Accountant (CPA) designation or have equivalent relevant education and experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are fluent in both French and English and can collaborate effectively with colleagues around the world.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You thrive in a fast-paced environment where you balance recurring monthly accounting activities with multiple ongoing projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What will make you stand out:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are recognized for your resourcefulness, adaptability, and proactive mindset.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You demonstrate strong attention to detail and consistently deliver accurate financial information on time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience collaborating across multiple finance functions and can approach challenges with a broad business perspective.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You enjoy identifying opportunities to improve, automate, and optimize existing processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Do you think you can bring this role to life? Send us your application, we want to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join the Coveolife!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We encourage all qualified candidates to apply regardless of, for example, age, gender, disability, gaps in CV, national or ethnic background.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;This job description was written by humans, assisted by AI. We may leverage technology in our hiring process to help us see the person behind the resume.&lt;/p&gt;
