&lt;h2&gt;Sell transformative AI solutions to some of the most innovative enterprises in EMEA.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;351&quot; data-end=&quot;545&quot;&gt;Are you passionate about the transformative power of artificial intelligence (AI)? Join Coveo and help bring cutting-edge AI solutions to leading enterprise organizations across the EMEA market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;547&quot; data-end=&quot;806&quot;&gt;At Coveo, we build AI-powered solutions that deliver hyper-relevant and personalized digital experiences. Our platform combines enterprise AI and generative AI to help businesses drive profitability while creating meaningful customer and employee experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;813&quot; data-end=&quot;870&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;813&quot; data-end=&quot;870&quot;&gt;As our Senior Enterprise Account Executive, you will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, engage, and develop relationships with enterprise clients across the EMEA region.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strategic account plans focused on delivering measurable business outcomes for customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with alliances managers and partners to generate and expand business opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead complex enterprise sales cycles from initial engagement through negotiation and closing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop compelling business cases and proposals that clearly articulate the value of Coveo’s platform.&lt;/li&gt;
