&lt;p&gt;Do you thrive at the intersection of data, systems, and partner-led growth?&lt;br&gt;As a Senior Partner Operations Analyst at Coveo, you’ll scale and optimize the programs, processes, and insights that power our global partner ecosystem and fuel revenue through alliances.&lt;/p&gt;
