&lt;li&gt;Lead, mentor, and grow a team of product marketers, setting clear direction and elevating execution standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and evolve the go-to-market strategy to drive acquisition and expansion across channels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop differentiated positioning and messaging grounded in customer, market, and competitive insights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner cross-functionally with Product, Sales, and Demand Generation to drive aligned execution and measurable pipeline impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Elevate sales enablement and customer storytelling to strengthen market presence and win rates&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Here is what will qualify you for the role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years in marketing, including 3–5+ years in product marketing within ecommerce or digital commerce&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience defining and executing go-to-market strategies with Product, Sales, and Marketing leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience leading or mentoring team members and driving performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong strategic thinking and ability to connect insights to business outcomes&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What will make you stand out:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
