&lt;li&gt;Experience influencing executive stakeholders and contributing to company-level strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical mindset with the ability to tie initiatives to pipeline and revenue impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional storytelling skills, translating complex concepts into clear, compelling narratives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
