&lt;h2&gt;Turn strategic partnerships into meaningful revenue growth.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What if your next role gave you the opportunity to build high-impact partnerships that directly contribute to business growth? Coveo is looking for a Partner Manager to help expand our partner ecosystem by generating opportunities, accelerating pipeline, and driving revenue through strategic consulting and integration partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll work closely with our alliances, sales, and marketing teams to identify high-potential partners, create joint go-to-market momentum, and help partners successfully position Coveo’s AI-powered solutions. This is an ideal opportunity for someone who thrives on relationship building, business development, and delivering measurable commercial results.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Please note that this is a 12-month contract position with the possibility of becoming a permanent.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
