&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the generation of partner-sourced pipeline within your assigned territory and partner portfolio.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, develop, and grow relationships with high-potential system integrator (SI) and global system integrator (GSI) partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive qualified opportunities from identification through sales engagement and progression, partnering closely with Coveo Account Executives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with partners to uncover new business opportunities, accelerate pipeline creation, and contribute to revenue growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with internal marketing and sales teams on partner campaigns, enablement initiatives, webinars, and events that generate demand and partner engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support partner onboarding, training, and certification efforts to strengthen partner capabilities and long-term success with Coveo’s solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Here is what will qualify you for the role&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/h4&gt;
