&lt;h2&gt;The best-kept secret in enterprise AI. Your job is to make sure it doesn&#39;t stay&lt;br&gt;that way.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Every agentic workflow in the enterprise depends on surfacing the right information at the right moment. That&#39;s what Coveo does. We&#39;re the AI-powered&amp;nbsp;search and discovery platform behind companies like Intel, Dell, and Abbott - and a recognized Magic Quadrant leader.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here&#39;s the problem: not enough of the market knows it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We haven&#39;t told our story the way a company at the center of the AI shift should. The customer proof is extraordinary, the product point of view is sharp, and the category is exploding - Gartner launches a new, second Magic Quadrant for AI-&amp;nbsp;Search soon. What&#39;s missing is an owner to pull it together into a narrative our&amp;nbsp;market can&#39;t ignore.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re putting real money behind it. We’ve just hired tier 1 PR agencies in the US and Canada - and that&#39;s only the start. Prove the model in North America, and the plan is to fund the same effort in other geographies. This is a chance to build a&amp;nbsp;global communications function from the ground up, with the investment and executive support to do it.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That&#39;s this role. You&#39;ll decide what Coveo says to the world, where it says it, and&amp;nbsp;how it sounds - and make sure the right buyers and media hear it.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As our Senior Director, Communications &amp;amp; Brand Narrative you&#39;ll own:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The narrative.&lt;/strong&gt; Shape a differentiated story connecting our product vision, the market shift, and what our customers achieve - and make it land with&amp;nbsp;enterprise buyers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A global function, built in stages. &lt;/strong&gt;Deploy the US and Canada agency&amp;nbsp;budget now, prove what works, then expand into Europe and Australia.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Getting us on the map.&lt;/strong&gt; Build the earned-media engine from the ground up&amp;nbsp;- top-tier business and tech press, podcasts, and the channels where our&lt;br&gt;buyers pay attention - and lead the agency partnerships that scale it&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer storytelling.&lt;/strong&gt; Turn our marquee customers into compelling,&amp;nbsp;repeatable proof points - not buried case studies, but stories people&amp;nbsp;remember.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Social and brand voice.&lt;/strong&gt; Own our social presence and give Coveo a voice&amp;nbsp;that&#39;s confident, credible, and worth following.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-functional narrative leadership.&lt;/strong&gt; Align marketing, product, and&amp;nbsp;sales behind one story - and arm our executives to tell it well.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The big moments. &lt;/strong&gt;Drive integrated communications around product&amp;nbsp;launches, Gartner MQs, partnerships, and major announcements.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Here is what will qualify you for the role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are genuinely curious about AI and excited to explain how it&#39;s reshaping&amp;nbsp;the enterprise.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are a creative storyteller who can translate complex technology into a&amp;nbsp;narrative people care about.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have built communications programs - you&#39;re energized by a blank canvas,&amp;nbsp;not waiting for a playbook to inherit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work fluidly across product, sales, and marketing rather than operating in&amp;nbsp;a “PR” silo.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Can balance strategy with execution - you&#39;ll set the vision and get the&amp;nbsp;placements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring deep experience in enterprise B2B technology or SaaS&amp;nbsp;communications, and kn

